Process called "check_pattern_constraints" that takes engine as ExpansionEngine and constraints as List[PatternConstraint] and bindings as Dictionary[String, Any] returns Boolean:
    Try:
        For each constraint in constraints:
            Let checker_function be engine.pattern_matcher.constraint_checkers[constraint.constraint_type] if engine.pattern_matcher.constraint_checkers contains constraint.constraint_type else default_constraint_checker
            
            If bindings contains constraint.variable:
                Let value be bindings[constraint.variable]
                If not checker_function with constraint as constraint and value as value:
                    Return false
        
        Return true
        
    Catch error:
        Return false

Process called "type_constraint_checker" that takes constraint as PatternConstraint and value as Any returns Boolean:
